StepConstr

public case StepConstr(ConstrRef ref,
                       NameAppl rel,
                       Expr expr);
Step constraint (DZ only).

Parameters:
ref - which step is referred to by the constraint.
rel - a binary Z relation describing how the referred step is related to the expr.
expr - expression denoting a number of steps which is related via rel with the referred step.

TimeConstr

public case TimeConstr(ConstrRef ref,
                       NameAppl rel,
                       Expr expr);
Real-time constraint (DZ only). Similar to StepConstr, with the only difference that instead of steps real-time is used.
